<div class="jumbotron text-center">
    <h1>Disaster Alleviation Foundation</h1>
    <h3 class="text-danger">Available Money: R @ViewBag.Available</h3>
    <h3 class="text-purple">Available Goods: @ViewBag.goodAvailable</h3>
    <p class="lead">Welcome to the Disaster Alleviation Foundation!</p>
    <p>Together, we stand committed to providing support and relief to those affected by disasters. Our mission is to make a positive impact on communities in times of crisis.</p>
    <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/Home/AllocationIndex">Allocations And Purchase</a></p>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2>Disaster</h2>
            <p>In times of disaster, the need for charitable efforts becomes even more crucial. We understand the gravity of these situations and strive to make a difference. Our dedicated team works tirelessly to provide aid, support, and hope to those affected.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-warning" href="/Home/ListDisaster">View Disasters</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2>Monetary Donations</h2>
            <p>At Monetary Donation Charity, we understand the profound impact that financial support can have on individuals and communities facing challenges.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-warning" href="/Home/MonetaryList">View Monetary Donations</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2>Good Donation</h2>
            <p>At Good Donation Charity, we believe in the power of giving to create positive change. With your support, we work towards improving the lives of those in need, whether it's providing essential supplies during disasters or supporting long-term community development projects.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-warning" href="/Home/GoodList">View Good Donations</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
